LeadParagraph: Emily Rose Heroy and Yale A. Fillingham are to be married Sunday evening in an outdoor ceremony at Millcreek Barns in Watervliet, Mich. Mariah P. Cunnick, a friend of the couple who became a Universal Life minister for the event, is to officiate.
